3. Key Features to Build (MVP)
  Agar poora Amazon nahi bana sakte, toh bas ye 3 complex features banao jo resume mein chamkein:

    1. Dynamic Pricing & Negotiation System:
        OLX jaisa chat system jaha price offer button ho.

    2. Distance-Based Matching:
        Hotel apna location daale aur sirf 50km radius ke farmers dikhein. (Ye dikhata hai tumhe Geo-spatial data aata hai).

    3. Inventory Expiry Logic:
        Agar Farmer ne HarvestDate 5 din purani daali hai, toh frontend pe "Low Quality/Old Stock" ka warning flag dikhana.



## AgriBridge ##

AgriBridge
│
├── client/                         # React Application
│   └── src/
